","msg":"東北三省又真係同北歐國家嘅緯度幾接近喎，比日本仲近過北極，唔怪得話自己有份"},{"pid":"25ae94f9e6aa17f6bfb1164bac744967316be291","tid":541550,"uid":21035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"babf9813fea44ef202e767223fafa1105f34244c","tid":541550,"uid":63909,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"1fee318563c83c1c1124b36ed4fa4a40c4509d93","tid":541550,"uid":32699,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T14:26:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【中國發布首份北極政策白皮書】<br />\n【指中國是陸上最接近北極圈國家之一】<br />\n【將參與開發利用北極航道等資源】<br />\n<br />\n北極圈距離北京大約三千公里，而中國發布的首份《中國的北極政策》白皮書，則形容中國是地緣上的「近北極國家」，亦是「陸上最接近北極圈的國家之一」，所以是北極事務的「重要利益攸關方」，必須認識、保護、利用和參與治理北極。<br />\n<br />\n有關「利用」的部分，白皮書點明，中國將參與開發利用北極航道、油氣、礦産等能源以及漁業和旅遊資源。而其中的北極航道，包括接壤加拿大的西北航道和接近北歐及俄羅斯的東北航道，其重要運輸價值，近年引來各國競爭。<br />\n<br />\n外交部副部長孔鉉佑不否認當中存在爭議，冀北極國家依據國際法管理北極航道，充分保障各國利用北極航道的權利和自由。<br />\n<br />\n白皮書亦強調中國尊重北極國家的主權和北極土著人的傳統，但國際社會一直有聲音，質疑中國的北極政策有戰略和軍事意圖，甚至要發展成「極地強國」。<br />\n<br />\n外交部回應指<span style=\"color: red;\">中國參與北極的開發利用，是對北極的貢獻，帶來的是發展的機遇，受惠的是北極地區的人民</span>，有關掠奪資源、破壞環境的擔心完全沒有必要，亦指中俄兩國有意願共同建設「冰上絲綢之路」，以切合今後「一帶一路」建設的需要。<br />\n<br />\n#陸上最接近北極圈的國家之一<br />\n#參與開發利用資源<br />\n#有關掠奪資源的擔心完全沒有必要<br />\n#建設冰上絲綢之路<br />\n#有冇考慮過北極熊感受<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1623171964493950/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F1623171964493950%2F&d=zXBzb8A%2FFZ0woOaTik%2FBGm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=87e13185\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1623171964493950/</a></blockquote><br />\n屌你老味又係呢D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T14:34:17.000Z","msg":"共匪次次喉住人地啲野都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T20:20:40.000Z","msg":"開放自由行係對香港嘅貢獻，帶來嘅係旅遊業發展嘅機遇，受惠嘅係香港地區嘅人民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f627a4d28f371079ad4a131364a64003826df1a","tid":541550,"uid":10890,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"e8ab92a48d5048aa901de5941e0dbc488c189521","tid":541550,"uid":65186,"like":0,"dislike":25,"score":-25,"quote":{"pid":"a9516b8fdd45581248bd51fda11cfeef9962bc43","tid":541550,"uid":90601,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T14:45:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/d/d8/ARCTIC_CIRCLE_021106.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fd%2Fd8%2FARCTIC_CIRCLE_021106.jpg&h=e4ef715d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T20:16:37.000Z","msg":"東北三省又真係同北歐國家嘅緯度幾接近喎，比日本仲近過北極，唔怪得話自己有份"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T20:26:33.000Z","msg":"你講笑定認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上面成個俄羅斯喺度喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3f2ae4c6799450ba3997a896c7a2e78c888c304","tid":541550,"uid":104443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T20:29:18.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯直程連國土都入埋北極圈入面喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc50d33d386fd75613d44015bdceac59b46a4338","tid":541550,"uid":65186,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"4f627a4d28f371079ad4a131364a64003826df1a","tid":541550,"uid":10890,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"e8ab92a48d5048aa901de5941e0dbc488c189521","tid":541550,"uid":65186,"like":0,"dislike":25,"score":-25,"quote":{"pid":"a9516b8fdd45581248bd51fda11cfeef9962bc43","tid":541550,"uid":90601,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T14:45:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/d/d8/ARCTIC_CIRCLE_021106.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwiki